---
// Code Example Section component
import PythonCodeBlock from './PythonCodeBlock.astro';
---

<section id="examples" class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-5 fade-in-up">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">See SPADE in Action</h2>
            <p class="lead text-muted">Creating intelligent agents has never been easier</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 slide-in-left">
                <PythonCodeBlock 
                    filename="agent_example.py"
                    showCopyButton={true}
                    code={`import spade
from spade.agent import Agent
from spade.behaviour import CyclicBehaviour
from spade.message import Message

class MyAgent(Agent):
    class MyBehaviour(CyclicBehaviour):
        async def run(self):
            msg = await self.receive(timeout=10)
            if msg:
                print(f"Message received: {msg.body}")
                reply = Message(to=str(msg.sender))
                reply.body = "I received your message!"
                await self.send(reply)

    async def setup(self):
        behaviour = self.MyBehaviour()
        self.add_behaviour(behaviour)

async def main():
    agent = MyAgent("agent@localhost", "password")
    await agent.start()

if __name__ == "__main__":
    spade.run(main())`}
                />
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 slide-in-right">
                <h3 class="mb-4">Simple & Intuitive API</h3>
                <p>SPADE provides a clean, object-oriented API that makes it easy to create powerful multi-agent systems. Define your agents, their behaviors, and how they communicate with just a few lines of code.</p>
                <p>This example shows a basic agent that can receive messages and automatically reply to them. SPADE handles all the underlying communication details for you.</p>
                <a href="https://spade-mas.readthedocs.io/en/latest/usage.html" class="btn btn-primary">View More Examples</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .code-example {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    /* Dark mode badge section and code example */
    :global(body.dark-mode) .code-example {
        background: var(--dark-card-bg) !important;
        border-color: var(--dark-border) !important;
    }
    
    .code-header {
        background: #f0f0f0;
        color: #333;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .code-body {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    
    /* Dark mode code body styles */
    :global(body.dark-mode) .code-header {
        background: #343a40;
        color: white;
        border-bottom-color: #4a5568;
    }
    :global(body.dark-mode) .code-body {
        background-color: #1a202c !important;
    }
    
    :global(body.dark-mode) .code-body pre {
        background-color: #1a202c !important;
        color: #e2e8f0 !important;
    }
    
    :global(body.dark-mode) .code-body code {
        color: #e2e8f0 !important;
    }
</style>
</section>
